insert into "books" ("description", "image_url", "title") values ('Lari, Layne and the Cat Colony is a book about a girl, her little brother and all the cats they have collected and given care to for several years. Lari is an eleven-year-old girl who from the womb has had a passionate love for cats. While pregnant with Lari, her mother could not understand why she constantly had dreams of cats and kittens. After meeting Lari, anyone can understand why. Layne is Lari''s seven-year-old brother who joins Lari at a young age to help her with her crusade for the cats. Once the cats have settled into Lari and Layne''s home lifestyle, each cat develops his/her own personality. Captured in their actual setting, you will get a visual for each cat and an understanding for their individualistic traits of existence. You will read and learn about why each cat comes to live with Lari and Layne, how Lari and Layne have cared for them, and what special things each cat has brought or done for the home. Each cat has his or her own story, and special quality that makes Lari and Layne''s mom crazy. But no matter how silly or mean the stunt, Lari and Layne''s mom keeps letting them add more and more cats to this special cat colony!', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=oC1R17uibqwC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 'Lari, Layne, & the Cat Colony');
