r Prize, and so I am qualified. Speaking in my official capacity as a Pulitzer Prize winner, Mr. Schneider, your movie sucks."', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=eipZqzyaF0UC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 'Your Movie Sucks');
